    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889120/extras/d83d1cebf71f49fd1808771f13eebce4.avif?t=1766064694\" width=200 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889120/extras/377c8ece8448d26c5025e0390d970b7c.poster.avif?t=1766064694\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889120/extras/377c8ece8448d26c5025e0390d970b7c.webm?t=1766064694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889120/extras/377c8ece8448d26c5025e0390d970b7c.mp4?t=1766064694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>隐身有不同的选择</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>制作和改进设备</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>赋予角色各种能力的灯笼</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889120/extras/c7bd1d02595e217fde2278ca54299381.avif?t=1766064694\" width=200 height=100 /></span><br>The Forked Road 是一个关于穿越一个死去的世界寻找一个可以称之为家的地方的故事。<br>一场神秘的大灾变，瞬间摧毁了几乎所有的生命，整个世界都被尘土覆盖。你是少数能活下来的人之一。你能适应新规则并找出灾难的原因吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889120/extras/a06e684184eb1542b4d1f149911de200.avif?t=1766064694\" width=200 height=100 /></span><br>The Forked Road 是一款潜行动作游戏，您的角色在其中极易受到敌人和环境的影响。<br>使用你的特殊能力、小工具和陷阱来达到你的目标。或者，也许你试图避免冲突？<br>在途中，您会遇到可以与之交谈的各种角色。与他们对话将帮助您更好地了解这个世界。",
